assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Sekisui Jushi Corporation provides products and services through the application of composite technology in Japan. The company offers traffic and scenery related products, including road surface indication materials, road signs, signatures, signboards, sound-proof wall materials, road safety materials, electronic system-related products, guard fences for walkers, guard fences for vehicles, storms, snow fences, car bumping posts, the assembling sidewalks, handrails, park materials, shelters, solar lightings, and artificial wood. It also provides sports facility related products, such as artificial turf field sprinkling systems; artificial turf field highway drainage systems; and artificial turf for school grounds, soccer, futsal, baseball, rugby, American football, field hockey, tennis, and landscape use. In addition, the company offers mesh fences, mekakushi walls, soundproofing mekakushi walls, vertical lattice fences, bicycle parking, and handrail products; and packing unity band films, packing materials, packing machines, safe fences, agriculture materials, and facilities gardening materials. Further, it provides other products consisting of concrete single exfoliation prevention systems, aluminum resin laminated compound boards, decoration building materials, assembling pipe systems, digital retrieval systems, and motor parts-related products. Sekisui Jushi Corporation was incorporated in 1941 and is headquartered in Osaka, Japan.
